<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="optimistic-adj">optimistic <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌɒptɪ'mɪstɪk/    美 /ˌɑːptɪ'mɪstɪk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>乐观的；抱乐观看法的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an optimistic estimate
乐观的估计</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I admire Helen because she is <strong>optimistic about</strong> life.
我敬佩海伦，因为她对生活积极乐观。</p><footer>2008 湖南书面表达</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>My good performance in the job interview left me optimistic <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ my future.  （2014 安徽改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. about  </p></div>